1. Go to- > File - > New -> Maven Project->Next
2. Select the org.apache.maven.archetypes with maven-archetype-webapp and click Next
3. Provide the Group id , Artifact id(file name) and click Finish, Maven web Project is created
4. Here the  project created , Check for index .jsp file containing Hello Welcome to maven web
5. In pom.xml add the dependencies as shown below.
6. To run the project right click and Run as Maven Clean - It clears out the existing classes  previous one . Here we can  see the console for Build Success.
7. Now again run the project right click  and Run as Maven Install – to add artifacts  to the project
8. Again run the project Maven test – to test the project
9. Now  run the project Run as Maven Build – it creates JAR/WAR files to the project
10. Here specify the goals -> they clean install test or Package ,click -> Apply & Run
11. Now run the project as Run on server 
12. Here we have to select the tomcat server 9.0 ,Click -> Finish
13  we can see output in browser
